```plantuml
@startuml spagnuolocarmine_serverless-computing-for-iot

actor IoT_Device as Device
participant "RabbitMQ (AMQP Broker)" as AMQP_Broker
participant "RabbitMQ (MQTT Broker)" as MQTT_Broker
participant "Nuclio Function (AMQP Producer)" as AMQP_Producer
participant "Nuclio Function (AMQP Consumer)" as AMQP_Consumer
participant "Nuclio Function (MQTT Producer)" as MQTT_Producer
participant "Nuclio Function (MQTT Consumer)" as MQTT_Consumer
participant Logger

Device -> AMQP_Broker: Send temperature data
AMQP_Broker -> AMQP_Producer: Receive temperature event
AMQP_Producer -> AMQP_Broker: Process and push event

AMQP_Broker -> AMQP_Consumer: Trigger function with temperature event
AMQP_Consumer -> Logger: Log temperature data

Device -> MQTT_Broker: Send temperature data
MQTT_Broker -> MQTT_Producer: Receive temperature event
MQTT_Producer -> MQTT_Broker: Process and push event

MQTT_Broker -> MQTT_Consumer: Trigger function with temperature event
MQTT_Consumer -> Logger: Log temperature data

@enduml
```